<HEADLINE> Auto-leasing Club to Operate out of Beijing Airport </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 17 (Xinhua) -- An auto-leasing company will
begin operations at Beijing's Capital International Airport.
</P>
<P>
Beijing Shijitong Auto Club and Beijing Shouqi Group
Corp. signed the agreement here today to form China's largest
professional auto-leasing company.
</P>
<P>
Experts said the agreement should help standardize the
country's auto-leasing market and make it more affordable.
</P>
<P>
