agenda and discuss means of activating cooperation in political,
economic, security and military spheres.
</P>
<P>
In a statement concluding the meeting, Kuwaiti First Deputy
Prime Minister and Foreign Minister Sheikh Sabah Al-Ahmad Al-Sabah
said that "I am pleased to express my happiness in reaching
positive results which will be reflected in the important
recommendations that will be submitted to" the summit.
</P>
<P>
On Tuesday, Kuwait expressed optimism that the forthcoming
summit will yield important results, deepen and strengthen
relations in all spheres among the member states, enhance their
march towards unity and realize the aspirations and interests of
their peoples. 
</P>
