<HEADLINE> Myanmar Party Urged to Play Constructive Role </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, December 18 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar authorities Thursday
urged the National League for Democracy (NLD) to play a
constructive role and cooperate with them in creating conditions
for an open discussion between them to take place and national
reconciliation to materialize.
</P>
