<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Index Up 11.22 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 18 (Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of Thailand
(SET) index Thursday gained 11.22 points from Wednesday to close
at 387.38.
</P>
<P>
Shares worth 3.369 billion baht (74.8 million US dollars)
changed hands Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The SET index Wednesday rose 5.88 points from Tuesday to close
at 376.16, with some 131 million shares worth 2.716 billion baht
(60 million dollars) traded in a total of 29,405 transactions.
</P>
