<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, December 17 (Xinhua) -- Atletico Mineiro of Brazil
played a 1-1 draw with Argentina's Lanus on Wednesday night in
Belo Horizonte to win the Conmebol Cup championship with a 5-2
aggregate score.
</P>
<P>
